[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1067","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1067.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1350","title":"ARCAD Systemhaus 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ARCAD Systemhaus 0.078-5 版本在安装关键程序和文件时设置了全局可写权限，本地攻击者可通过替换程序为特洛伊木马，从而获取系统权限。该漏洞影响 ARCAD Systemhaus 0.078-5 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1350"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-29","updated":"1999-09-29","remediation":"升级到 ARCAD Systemhaus 的最新版本，或手动修复受影响文件和目录的权限设置，确保关键程序和文件仅对授权用户可写。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93871933521519&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1067.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0789","title":"IBM AIX ftpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3.2 的 FTP 服务守护进程 ftpd 调用的 libc 标准库函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 FTP 端口发送特制的请求数据包触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行，实现完全控制目标主机。该漏洞远程可利用、无需认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0789"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.690","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本（如 5.3/6.1/7.x），或安装 APAR IX87162 补丁。AIX 4.3.2 已停止维护，应迁移至受支持版本。临时缓解措施：编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 ftpd 行后执行 refresh -s inetd 禁用 FTP 服务，改用 SSH/SFTP 进行文件传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-072.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/679","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19532","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0789.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0789.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0789","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0789.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0789.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/44d84714e9a3b4364d62f8189e2d74dba61b570e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-25cr-8qvj-rg6f/GHSA-25cr-8qvj-rg6f.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/ftp.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/aix_ftpd.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0789.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0709.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1069","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1069.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1352","title":"Linux Kernel mknod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux 2.2 内核中的 mknod 系统调用在处理符号链接时存在安全缺陷，未正确验证目标文件路径是否为符号链接，导致本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接并调用 mknod 覆盖系统关键文件，从而提升权限或破坏系统完整性。攻击者需拥有本地用户权限，无需其他特殊条件即可利用该漏洞实施权限提升攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1352"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.463","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在 2.3.x 开发版中修复。如无法升级内核，可通过 LSM（Linux Security Module）如 SELinux 或 AppArmor 限制普通用户执行 mknod 系统调用权限，并设置 /proc/sys/fs/protected_hardlinks 为 1 增强链接保护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93855134409747&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1352.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1352","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1352.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1352.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x7c6-rhq3-252p/GHSA-x7c6-rhq3-252p.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1352.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000795.txt","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1069.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1069.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0737","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0737.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0940","title":"Mutt mutt邮件客户端 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"mutt 邮件客户端在处理恶意构造的 MIME 消息时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制邮件触发溢出，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 mutt 邮件客户端多个历史版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击无需身份认证且复杂度低。建议用户升级至已修复版本以消除风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0940"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.293","remediation":"建议升级 mutt 邮件客户端至 1.0.1 版本或更高版本（已于 1999 年发布修复版本），通过包管理器执行升级：Debian/Ubuntu 执行 `apt-get update && apt-get install mutt`，RedHat/CentOS 执行 `yum update mutt`，或从官网 http://www.mutt.org 下载 1.0.1 及以上版本源码编译安装。若无法立即升级，可临时禁用 MIME 处理功能（在 .muttrc 中设置 `set mime_forward=no` 和 `set mime_forward_rest=no`）作为临时缓解措施，但强烈建议尽快升级至修复版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0940"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0737.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0522","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0522.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0788","title":"Knox Software Arkeia nlserverd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Knox Software Arkeia 备份软件中的 nlserverd 守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标系统开放的特制端口发送超长字符串触发服务崩溃。该漏洞影响 Arkeia 4.0/4.1 版本，部署在多种操作系统平台上。未经身份验证的远程攻击者无需任何凭据即可利用此漏洞，只需向 nlservd 监听端口发送构造好的长字符串即可导致服务中断，造成拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0788"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.567","remediation":"升级 Knox Software Arkeia 至 4.2 或更高版本，厂商已修复 nlservd 缓冲溢出及远程拒绝服务漏洞；如无法立即升级，应移除 /usr/knox/bin/nlservd 和 /usr/knox/bin/rnavc 的 SUID 权限（chmod u-s），并在防火墙中限制对 nlservd 服务端口的访问，仅允许受信任的管理主机连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837184228248&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/662","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7af4f92412aedbb5d40436f8e5560c660110d48c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0788.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0788","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0788.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0788.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/275b64282d615395506db2a6db24fd5fa8ac8f24/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-29xc-rhpj-gjp7/GHSA-29xc-rhpj-gjp7.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/dos.rules","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0788.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.193"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0522.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1068","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1068.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1351","title":"KVIrc IRC客户端 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"KVIrc IRC 客户端 0.9.0 版本在处理 DCC GET 请求时存在目录遍历漏洞。当用户启用了 \"Listen to !nick <soundname> requests\" 选项后，远程攻击者可通过向目标 IRC 客户端发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 DCC GET 请求，突破文件路径限制，实现任意文件读取。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞窃取目标系统上的敏感文件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1351"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.337","remediation":"升级 KVIrc 至 1.0.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，请在「设置」→「选项」→「IRC」→「高级」中取消勾选「Listen to !nick &lt;soundname&gt; requests」选项以禁用该功能，并避免在不可信频道中接受 DCC 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93845560631314&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7761.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8p4w-cwr7-jq9h/GHSA-8p4w-cwr7-jq9h.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000790.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1909","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1909.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1484","title":"Microsoft MSN Messenger Service 1.0 Setup BBS ActiveX Control 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft MSN Messenger Service 1.0 的 Setup BBS ActiveX 控件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造特制网页并诱使用户访问，触发 ActiveX 控件中的缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者能够在受影响系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 MSN Messenger Service 1.0 版本，攻击条件为用户使用 Internet Explorer 访问恶意网页，危害等级高危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1484"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-24","updated":"1999-09-24","remediation":"立即卸载 MSN Messenger Service 1.0 及关联的 Setup BBS ActiveX 控件，该产品已停止支持且不再接收安全更新。在 Internet Explorer 中禁用 ActiveX 控件执行（将 Internet 区域安全级别设为高，并启用「ActiveX 控件和插件」下的「禁用」策略）。建议迁移至 Microsoft Teams 或 Skype 等受支持的即时通讯方案。如因兼容性必须保留，请在组策略中设置 Kill Bit 禁用 CLSID 以阻止 ActiveX 控件在浏览器中实例化。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19516"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1909.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1909.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1909.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0705","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0705.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0906","title":"SUSE Linux sscw HOME 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"S.u.S.E. Linux 6.2 系统中的 sccw 程序存在基于 HOME 环境变量的缓冲区溢出漏洞。具有本地访问权限的攻击者可设置超长 HOME 环境变量，触发 sccw 中的缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞仅需本地用户权限即可利用，影响 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0906"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.170","remediation":"升级 S.u.S.E. Linux 至 6.3 及以上版本，或在 SUSE 官方补丁发布后立即安装。临时缓解措施：使用 `chmod -s /usr/bin/sscw` 移除 sscw 的 setuid 位，或直接卸载 sscw 软件包，限制本地普通用户执行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/656","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19508"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0705.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0710","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0710.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0908","title":"Sun Solaris TCP Stream Driver mutex_enter 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris TCP 流驱动程序存在 mutex_enter 递归调用导致的拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过建立恶意 TCP 连接向目标系统发送特制数据流，触发驱动程序中互斥锁的递归调用，导致内核 panic 崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1/2.6/7.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0908"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.417","remediation":"升级至 Sun 安全补丁 107081-03（Solaris 2.5.1/2.6）或 107080-03（Solaris 7.0）以修复 mutex_enter 递归调用导致的拒绝服务。如无法立即打补丁，可在网关或主机防火墙层面限制对受影响端口的非信任来源 TCP 连接作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/655","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19507"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0710.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0863","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0863.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1013","title":"IBM AIX named-xfer 文件覆盖本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 4.1.5 及 4.2.1 版本中的 named-xfer 工具存在文件覆盖漏洞。系统组成员（system group）可通过向 named-xfer 传递 `-f` 参数配合特制的畸形 zone 文件，覆盖系统关键文件，从而将权限提升至 root。攻击者只需具备 system 组权限即可利用，无需认证，危害较大。IBM 未提供官方补丁，建议禁用或限制 named-xfer 的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1013"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.357","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.3.3 或更高版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 (IX86565)。如无法升级，移除 named-xfer 的 setuid root 权限 (chmod u-s /usr/sbin/named-xfer)，并将系统组成员审查清理，确保只有可信任用户属于 system 组。同时限制 named-xfer -f 参数的使用，通过文件权限控制 zone 文件仅允许 root 写入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837026726954&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/673","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1013","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1013.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-958c-wvqf-f46f/GHSA-958c-wvqf-f46f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/673/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0863.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1126","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1126.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1477","title":"Mandriva Linux GNOME 库 espeaker 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"GNOME 库 1.0.8 版本中存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，当程序（如 nethack）处理超长的 --espeaker 命令行参数时，未正确检查输入长度，导致栈缓冲区溢出。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞覆盖返回地址，以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Mandriva Linux Mandrake 6.0 及使用 GNOME Libs 1.0.8 的系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1477"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.527","remediation":"升级 GNOME 库至 1.0.9 或更高版本，该版本已修复 espeaker 参数缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，建议移除 nethack 等受影响程序的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/games/nethack），限制本地普通用户执行提权操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/28717","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/663","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3349","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19512"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1126.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0708","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0708.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0777","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Server (IIS) 4.0 及 Microsoft Commercial Internet System (MCIS) 2.5 中的 FTP 服务存在权限绕过漏洞。该漏洞源于 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 之后发布的热修复补丁引入的回归错误，导致 FTP 服务器未能正确执行 NTFS 文件系统的\"无访问\"权限设置。远程攻击者可通过浏览器匿名访问目标 FTP 服务器，读取甚至删除本应被禁止访问的文件，造成敏感信息泄露或数据破坏。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞，CVSS v2.0 评分为 7.5，危害等级高。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS99-039 中发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0777"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-23","updated":"1999-09-23","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-039 提供的补丁程序（对应 KB 文章 Q241407/Q242559），该补丁修复了 IIS 4.0 和 MCIS 2.5 中 FTP 权限绕过问题。如运行 Windows NT 4.0，应升级至 Service Pack 5 或更高版本。对于仍在使用的旧系统，建议迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）并启用最新安全更新。临时缓解措施：在 FTP 站点上禁用匿名访问，并对敏感目录设置 NTFS 文件系统权限而非仅依赖 IIS 权限控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e7c7f7ae9af22de7901413e757a1767cf5623277/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0777.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0777","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0777.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0777.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qjvq-8mcw-xc4h/GHSA-qjvq-8mcw-xc4h.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0777.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0777.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0519","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0519.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0786","title":"Sun Solaris 动态链接器 LD_PROFILE 本地文件创建漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 动态链接器在处理 LD_PROFILE 环境变量时存在不安全文件创建漏洞。本地攻击者可通过结合符号链接攻击，在运行 setuid 或 setgid 程序时触发动态链接器以特权身份创建恶意文件，从而可能导致权限提升或系统文件被覆写。攻击前提是拥有本地 shell 访问权限，利用难度较低。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0786"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.317","remediation":"建议升级至 Solaris 7 及以上版本（该漏洞在 Solaris 7 中已修复），或安装 Sun 安全补丁 106541-13 及后续版本。如无法立即升级，可通过限制普通用户设置 LD_PROFILE 环境变量（在 /etc/system 中配置并重启）作为临时缓解措施，或移除 prof(1) 的 setuid 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/659","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19509"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0519.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0712","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0712.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0912","title":"FreeBSD VFS缓存本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.0/3.1/3.2 版本的 VFS 缓存（vfs_cache）存在拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过打开大量文件耗尽系统缓存资源，导致系统性能严重下降甚至崩溃。该漏洞利用条件简单，无需特殊权限即可触发，影响 FreeBSD 3.x 系列多个版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0912"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.920","remediation":"升级到 FreeBSD 3.3 或更高版本，此版本已修复 vfs_cache 因大量打开文件导致的内核内存耗尽问题。如无法升级，可通过 `sysctl -w kern.maxfiles=N` 限制单进程最大文件打开数，或在 `/etc/sysctl.conf` 中设置 `kern.maxfiles=2048` 和 `kern.maxfilesperproc=1024` 降低影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1079","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/653","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19505"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0712.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0297","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0297.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0708","title":"Martin Schulze Cfingerd GECOS 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"cfingerd 1.4.2 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向 GECOS 字段提交超长输入触发栈溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Martin Schulze Cfingerd 1.4.2 及更早版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低。成功利用后攻击者可完全控制目标系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0708"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.557","remediation":"立即升级 cfingerd 至 1.4.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复 GECOS 字段长度检查逻辑。如无法升级，可在 /etc/cfingerd.conf 中限制本地用户登录或禁用 cfingerd 服务，改用安全替代方案如 inetutils-inetd 的 fingerd。同时建议使用 AppArmor/SELinux 限制 cfingerd 进程权限，降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/651","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19504","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0708.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0708","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0708.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0708.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3rpm-2rjq-r29f/GHSA-3rpm-2rjq-r29f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cfinger_format_bug.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0708.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990806.data"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0297.toml"}]